<p>kept me late awake, but by concentrating my thoughts on elevating topics I was asleep before bombs were dropped.  One fell fairly near, but there was no danger to speak of.</p>
<p>Fritz has had his daily shell today, mostly concussion H.E. &amp; a little nearer us, but nothing to worry about.</p>
<p>The noisy crowd held a lesson in bomb throwing in the tent at about 1.30 this morning accompanied with taking the pin out, - a rather dangerous proceeding for drunks; &amp; then</p>
